# CRUD Application

A professional CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) system for managing client records. This application provides a complete client management solution with a MySQL database backend, server-side PHP operations, and a responsive user interface. It demonstrates fundamental database operations, form validation, and secure data handling practices.

